text: Her swutelað on ðysan gewrite þæt Godwine geann Leofwine readan ðæs dænnes æt Swiðrædingdænne on ece yrfe to habbanne & to sellanne on dæge & æfter dæge ðam ðe him leofost sy æt þon sceatte ðe Leofsunu him geldan scolde, þæt is feowertig penega & twa pund & eahta ambra cornes.
Nu ann Leofwine þæs dænnes ðon ðe Boctun to handa gega æfter his dæge.
Nu is þyses to gewittnesse, Lyfingc bisceop & Ælfmær abbud & se hired æt Cristescyrcean & se hired æt sancte Augustine & Sired & Ælfsige cild & Æþelric & manig oþer god man binnan byrig & butan.
